## How to Update
- New endpoint added? → Add row to the appropriate resource group table
- Endpoint changed? → Update the relevant row (Method, Path, Auth, Body, Response, Description)
- Endpoint removed? → Remove row from the table
- Auth method changed? → Update Authentication section
- New resource group? → Add a new table section

## Find It Fast
```bash
grep -r "@router\." src/api/           # All route definitions (FastAPI)
grep -r "app\.\(get\|post\|put\|delete\)" src/  # All routes (Express/Flask)
```
